      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY SCAR (4) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split and ran away with a 4.5 lengths win at this track over 400m in 22.45. Expected to go well again. LAMBRICK ROAD (7) resumed in a Grade 4/5 at this track and ran into the frame when second over 400m (22.75). Form here sound including two wins. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Leading chance. BUFFALO COWBOY (2) was out of in the placings when eighth last time but three runs back produced a handy 19.77 win over 350m at Traralgon. Expected to feature on best figures. FLYING MAVERICK (1) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (22.06), beaten 1.3 lengths. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Deserves a win and gets his chance.",
